rs]]\n[[Category:Burials at Schaerbeek Cemetery]]\n[[Category:Acad\u00e9mie Royale des Beaux-Arts alumni]]\n", "name_user": "175.36.24.156", "label": "unsafe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ren%C3%A9_Magritte"}
